These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip
2 different pets are kept: bird, hamster
1. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
2. the owner of the hamster is not the bongani-smoker##6
3. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage   | sprite      | soy-milk    |
| Food       | bongani       | oliveros    |
| Hobby      | tulip     | daffodil |
| Job        | bird | hamster     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different games are played: canasta, snooker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, funk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, indian
1. the fan disco is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the italian is not the person playing snooker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | snooker | canasta         |
| Movie-Genre   | disco      | funk |
| Sport         | skiing      | volleyball  |
| Transport     | indian        | italian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-3::.
