2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, game
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, tennis
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, july
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
2. the game-smoker is not the person drinking 7up##6
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | 7up        |
| Hobby         | game | siglo |
| Movie-Genre   | tennis      | volleyball |
| Transport     | june    | july |

