.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-4::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, domino
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, green
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, roller
1. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
2. the software-developer is not the person playing domino##6
3. the person who likes turquise is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | monopoly | domino      |
| Nationality   | green      | turquise |
| Sport         | software-developer     | architect  |
| Transport     | roller     | airplane  |

