.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, singing
City: london, boston
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, golf
House: colonial, cape-cod
1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
2. the person who's sport is badminton is not the cape-cod house##6
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | singing |
| Job           | boston | london  |
| Movie-Genre   | golf | badminton |
| Pet           | cape-cod     | colonial     |

